<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333;">
  <h2 style="color: #4CAF50;">New Project Created Successfully</h2>
  <p>Dear {{username}},</p>

  <p>We are excited to inform you that a new project has been created in your
    account:</p>

  <table style="border-collapse: collapse; margin: 10px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Project Name:</strong></td>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">{{projectName}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Creation Date:</strong></td>
      <td style="padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">{{creationDate}}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <p>You can view and manage your project by clicking the link below:</p>

  <a
    href="{{projectLink}}"
    style="
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        margin: 10px 0;
        color: #ffffff;
        background-color: #4CAF50;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
    "
  >View Project</a>

  <p>If you did not create this project or if you have any questions, please
    contact our support team immediately.</p>

  <p>Best regards,<br />{{companyName}} Team</p>

  <p style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #777;">Need help? Visit our support page or
    reply to this email.</p>
</div>